text: Marina Canetta Gobbi (born 1 April 1989 in São Paulo) is a female Brazilian recurve archer. She competed in the archery competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Brazilian female archers Category:Living people Category:1989 births Category:Archers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic archers of Brazil Category:South American Games silver medalists for Brazil Category:South American Games medalists in archery Category:Competitors at the 2014 South American Games
